# Your On Demand Food Ordering Solutions

A full-stack online food ordering web application built using React.js, Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB.

## Features
- User Login & Signup
- Browse Restaurants
- Browse Food Items
- Add to Cart
- Place Orders
- Admin Dashboard

## Technologies
- React.js
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- JWT
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
